- they use repos transaction functions, instead of fs ones
- they work :-)

author: cmpilato
msg: Make 'svn log filename' work over ra-dav when 'filename' no longer
exists in HEAD.  This re-closes issues #1423.
* subversion/libsvn_ra_dav/log.c
(svn_ra_dav__get_log): WWFD (what would the filesystem do?).  Try to
find the path at the largest of two revisions passed to the
function.
* subversion/clients/cmdline/log-cmd.c
(svn_cl__log): Make 'svn log' without revision parameters default to
BASE:1, not HEAD:1.
